<p><span class="anchor" id="p49"></span>وَهُوَ حسي كصغر وَمرض<a href="#p49" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p50"></span>يمْنَع كل مِنْهُمَا الْوَطْء<a href="#p50" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
